snippet.title: Sword Art Online Last Recollection - Story Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Welcome, everyone, to the Dark Territory.

Kirito and his allies come together with strong blades and stronger hearts to battle the forces of darkness when SWORD ART ONLINE Last Recollection launches on PS5 and PS4 on October 6, 2023!

Digital Pre-orders are available now

Every Digital Pre-order includes the Black Swordsman Weapons Skin Set pre-order bonus featuring iconic weapons from the SWORD ART ONLINE series!

#SWORDARTONLINE #LASTRECOLLECTION
